Task
Is it true that the given number is a positive odd number?
Given an arbitrary number. Determine if it is a positive odd number.
Create a variable number and assign it the value of an arbitrary integer. 
Create a variable isPositiveOdd and assign it a boolean expression that evaluates to true if the number is odd and positive and false otherwise.

Solution
const number = 21;
const isPositiveOdd = number % 2 !== 0 && number > 0;
